<br>
I am a Creature Handler, and as such use Mask Scent to sneak up on lairs and additionally, until recently, used the Scouting XP to indicate when I was 'sniffed' by the critters.<br>
<br>
If there were 3 aggressive critters, I would see 3 Scouting XP indications and that lets me know that I can now browse among them at will.<br>
<br>
Well, now I have maxxed out my Scouting XP and no longer get indication that I have been 'sniffed'. I cant surrender hunting or exploration to use up XP, as it is a requirement for CH...any suggestions?<br>
<br>
